patchouli
=========
Patchouli is a standalone Python script that help bridges Bangumi
(https://bgm.tv/) and Calibre (https://calibre-ebook.com/).
The script itself is used for grouping multiple manga file as a serie,
filling necessary metadata and adding them to Calibre library in batch.


Requirement
===========
* Python 3+ (Only tested with Python 3.13.7 under GNU/Linux).
* Calibre 8+ (Only tested with Calibre 8.7)


Recommended Workflow
====================
First step is to correct the filesystem, with each directory as a serie,
each manga as a file inside it.

For example:

    演员夜凪景 act-age - マツキタツヤ×宇佐崎しろ [Vol.01-Vol.12 + 108-123 话]/
        * 演员夜凪景 act-age - Vol.01.zip
        * 演员夜凪景 act-age - Vol.02.zip
        * 演员夜凪景 act-age - Vol.03.zip
        * 演员夜凪景 act-age - Vol.04.zip
        * 演员夜凪景 act-age - Vol.05.zip
        * 演员夜凪景 act-age - Vol.06.zip
        * 演员夜凪景 act-age - Vol.07.zip
        * 演员夜凪景 act-age - Vol.08.zip
        * 演员夜凪景 act-age - Vol.09.zip
        * 演员夜凪景 act-age - Vol.10.zip
        * 演员夜凪景 act-age - Vol.11.zip
        * 演员夜凪景 act-age - Vol.12.zip
        * 演员夜凪景 act-age - Chap.108-Chap.123.zip

    只有我不存在的城市-三部敬/
        * 只有我不存在的城市 - 卷01.epub
        * 只有我不存在的城市 - 卷02.epub
        * 只有我不存在的城市 - 卷03.epub
        * 只有我不存在的城市 - 卷04.epub
        * 只有我不存在的城市 - 卷05.epub
        * 只有我不存在的城市 - 卷06.epub
        * 只有我不存在的城市 - 卷07.epub
        * 只有我不存在的城市 - 卷08.epub
        * 只有我不存在的城市 - 卷09.epub

As example shown above, all the mangas should be grouped into same directory as
a serie. The directory name will be used when searching the manga metadata, so
it is recommended to use title that can be shown as first result in bangumi.
Additional comment should be placed inside bracket, patchouli will exclude them
in search text.

Each manga have their own volume metadata, patchouli will also help find that
information. User should attach volume number as filename suffix. Following
forms are supported:

    * ... - 卷01...
    * ... - 卷 01...
    * ... - Vol.01...
    * ... - Vol01...
    * ... - Vol 01...
    * ... - 01...

All the volume information must follows the half-width dash ("-") character.
Only on above cases, patchouli will know that this book is the first release of
the serie, and thus know where to find its metadata.
